# HTML INPUTS

Categories of inputs
	general inputs
		commonly used in forms to collect user information
		<input type="text">
		<input type="email">
		<input type="button">
		<input type="submit">
		<input type="number">
		<input type="password">
		<input type="reset">
		<input type="tel">
	duration inputs
		<input type="date">
		<input type="month">
		<input type="week">
		<input type="time">
		<input type="datetime-local">
	media inputs
		<input type="file">
		<input type="image"
	option inputs
		<input type="radio">
		<input type="checkbox">
		<input type=range">
	advanced inputs
		<input type="hidden">
		<input type="color">
		<input type="url">
		<input type="search">

